---
// Astro Component
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Free: The Cold Traffic Prompt Kit · ExpatBuildr</title>
<meta name="description" content="Get the exact prompt that generates a full lead generation post strategy for X, LinkedIn, Reddit, TikTok, Instagram, and YouTube — plus instant access to the strategy dashboard." />

<!-- Open Graph / Facebook -->
<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
<meta property="og:url" content="https://expatbuildr.com/free" />
<meta property="og:title" content="Free: The Cold Traffic Prompt Kit · ExpatBuildr" />
<meta property="og:description" content="Get the exact prompt that generates a full lead generation post strategy for X, LinkedIn, Reddit, TikTok, Instagram, and YouTube — plus instant access to the strategy dashboard." />
<meta property="og:image" content="https://expatbuildr.com/images/og-cold-traffic-prompt.png" />

<!-- Twitter -->
<meta property="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
<meta property="twitter:url" content="https://expatbuildr.com/free" />
<meta property="twitter:title" content="Free: The Cold Traffic Prompt Kit · ExpatBuildr" />
<meta property="twitter:description" content="Get the exact prompt that generates a full lead generation post strategy for X, LinkedIn, Reddit, TikTok, Instagram, and YouTube — plus instant access to the strategy dashboard." />
<meta property="twitter:image" content="https://expatbuildr.com/images/og-cold-traffic-prompt.png" />

<script is:inline>
  const theme = (() => {
    if (typeof localStorage !== 'undefined' && localStorage.getItem('theme')) {
      return localStorage.getItem('theme');
    }
    return 'dark'; // default for this funnel
  })();
  if (theme === 'light') {
    document.documentElement.classList.add('light');
  } else {
    document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
  }
</script>

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500;600&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --bg:       #050505;
    --bg-2:     #0a0a0a;
    --bg-3:     #111;
    --border:   rgba(255,255,255,.07);
    --border-hi:rgba(255,255,255,.14);
    --text:     #f0ede8;
    --text-muted:#9a9490;
    --text-dim: #5a5652;
    --accent-1: #a8e6a3;
    --accent-2: #c084fc;
    --accent-3: #f472b6;
    --amber:    #e8a020;
    --amber-dim:rgba(232,160,32,.2);
    --amber-glow:rgba(232,160,32,.06);
    --locked:   rgba(255,255,255,.03);
    --serif:    'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;
    --mono:     'DM Mono', monospace;
    --sans:     'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  }

  html.light {
    --bg:       #f8fafc;
    --bg-2:     #f1f5f9;
    --bg-3:     #ffffff;
    --border:   rgba(15,23,42,.08);
    --border-hi:rgba(15,23,42,.12);
    --text:     #0f172a;
    --text-muted:#475569;
    --text-dim: #64748b;
    --locked:   rgba(15,23,42,.03);
    --accent-1: #15803d;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── NOISE OVERLAY  /* noise */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed; inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; opacity: .5;
  }
  html.light body::before { opacity: 0.15; }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: rgba(5,5,5,.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
  }
  html.light nav { background: rgba(252,252,252,.92); }
  .nav-inner {
    max-width: 1060px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: .9rem clamp(1.25rem,5vw,2.5rem);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .nav-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .65rem; text-decoration: none; }
  .logo-mark {
    width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 6px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .logo-text {
    font-family: var(--sans); font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -.02em; color: var(--text);
  }
  .logo-text span { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-1), var(--accent-2)); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; font-weight: 300; }
  .nav-badge {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .6rem; letter-spacing: .12em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-2);
    background: rgba(192,132,252,.1);
    padding: .3em .7em;
  }
  #themeToggleBtn {
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    transition: all .2s;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
  }
  #themeToggleBtn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.05); transform: scale(1.1); }
  html.light #themeToggleBtn:hover { background: rgba(15,23,42,.05); }

  #themeToggleBtn .sun-icon { display: inline; color: #fbbf24; }
  #themeToggleBtn .moon-icon { display: none; color: #6366f1; }
  html.light #themeToggleBtn .sun-icon { display: none; }
  html.light #themeToggleBtn .moon-icon { display: inline; }
  html.light .nav-badge, 
  html.light .dash-card-tag { 
    color: var(--accent-1); 
    font-weight: 600; 
    border-color: rgba(21,128,61,.2); 
  }
  html.light .submit-btn { 
    color: #0f172a; 
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  #hero {
    padding: clamp(4rem,10vw,7rem) 0 clamp(2.5rem,6vw,4rem);
    position: relative; z-index: 5;
  }

  /* radial glow behind hero */
  #hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -100px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 700px; height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(168,230,163,.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .wrap { max-width: 1060px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 clamp(1.25rem,5vw,2.5rem); position: relative; z-index: 5; }

  .free-tag {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .5rem;
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .65rem; letter-spacing: .15em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent-1); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .free-tag::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-1), var(--accent-2), var(--accent-3));
    animation: pulse 2s ease infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)} 50%{opacity:.4;transform:scale(.7)} }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem,6.5vw,4.75rem);
    line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -.025em;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem; max-width: 22ch;
  }
  h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent-1); }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8; max-width: 52ch;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem; font-weight: 300;
  }

  .what-you-get {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .5rem 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .what-item {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .4rem;
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .65rem; letter-spacing: .06em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .what-item::before { content: '✓'; color: var(--accent-1); }

  /* ── CAPTURE BOX ── */
  .capture-box {
    background: var(--bg-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-hi);
    padding: clamp(1.75rem,4vw,2.5rem);
    max-width: 540px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .capture-box::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg,var(--accent-1),var(--accent-2),var(--accent-3));
  }

  .capture-label {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .6rem; letter-spacing: .15em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .capture-headline {
    font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.35rem; line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: .5rem;
  }
  .capture-sub {
    font-size: .82rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .field-wrap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .75rem; }

  .email-input {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: var(--bg-3);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-hi);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: .82rem;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color .15s;
    min-height: 44px;
  }
  .email-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent-2); }
  .email-input::placeholder { color: var(--text-dim); }

  .submit-btn {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1rem 1.4em;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent-1),var(--accent-2),var(--accent-3));
    color: #fff;
    min-height: 44px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: .78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: .1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .15s;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: .5rem;
  }
  .submit-btn:hover:not(:disabled) { filter: brightness(1.1); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .submit-btn:disabled { opacity: .5; cursor: not-allowed; }

  .capture-privacy {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .6rem; color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-top: .75rem; letter-spacing: .04em;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .msg { display: none; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .68rem; margin-top: .5rem; }
  .msg.error { color: #ef4444; }
  .msg.success { color: var(--accent-1); }

  /* ── WHAT YOU GET ── */
  #what {
    padding: clamp(3rem,7vw,5rem) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    position: relative; z-index: 5;
  }

  .section-tag {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .62rem; letter-spacing: .15em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-dim);
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .section-tag::after { content: ''; display: block; height: 1px; width: 3rem; background: var(--border-hi); }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.7rem,3.5vw,2.75rem);
    line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: .75rem;
  }
  h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent-1); }

  .deliverable-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .deliv-item {
    background: var(--bg-2);
    padding: 1.75rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: background .2s;
  }
  .deliv-item:hover { background: var(--bg-3); }

  .deliv-icon {
    font-size: 1.35rem; margin-bottom: .75rem; display: block;
  }
  .deliv-platform {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .6rem; letter-spacing: .12em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: .4rem;
  }
  .deliv-item h3 {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .88rem; font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text); margin-bottom: .4rem;
  }
  .deliv-item p {
    font-size: .8rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* DASHBOARD PREVIEW */
  .dashboard-preview {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-hi);
    background: var(--bg-2);
    padding: clamp(1.5rem,4vw,2.5rem);
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .dashboard-preview::before {
    content: 'DASHBOARD PREVIEW';
    position: absolute; top: 1rem; right: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .55rem; letter-spacing: .15em;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .dash-label {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .62rem; letter-spacing: .12em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent-1); margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .dash-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
    gap: .75rem;
  }
  .dash-card {
    background: var(--bg-3);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
  }
  .dash-card-platform {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .58rem; letter-spacing: .12em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: .35rem;
  }
  .dash-card-title {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .75rem; color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: .3rem; line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .dash-card-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .55rem; letter-spacing: .1em;
    text-transform: uppercase; padding: .15em .5em;
    background: rgba(192,132,252,.1); color: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-2);
  }

  /* ── WHY FREE ── */
  #why {
    padding: clamp(3rem,7vw,5rem) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    position: relative; z-index: 5;
  }
  .why-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .why-text p {
    font-size: .92rem; color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .why-text strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }
  .why-stat-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  .stat-row {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg-2);
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 2.2rem;
    color: var(--accent-1); line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .stat-desc { font-size: .8rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; }
  .stat-desc strong { color: var(--text); display: block; margin-bottom: .15rem; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .72rem; letter-spacing: .06em; }

  /* ── BOTTOM CTA ── */
  #bottom-cta {
    padding: clamp(3.5rem,8vw,6rem) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative; z-index: 5;
  }
  #bottom-cta::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 600px; height: 300px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top, rgba(168,230,163,.05) 0%, transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  #bottom-cta h2 { max-width: none; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
  #bottom-cta p { color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 48ch; margin: 0 auto 2rem; font-size: .92rem; }

  .cta-capture {
    max-width: 440px; margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .75rem;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    position: relative; z-index: 5;
  }
  .footer-inner {
    max-width: 1060px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(1.25rem,5vw,2.5rem);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem;
  }
  .footer-brand { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .62rem; color: var(--text-dim); letter-spacing: .06em; }
  .footer-brand span { color: var(--accent-1); }
  .footer-links { list-style: none; display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .footer-links a { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .6rem; color: var(--text-dim); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; transition: color .15s; }
  .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--accent-3); }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  .fade-up {
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px);
    transition: opacity .55s ease, transform .55s ease;
  }
  .fade-up.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  .fade-1 { animation: fadeUp .6s ease .05s forwards; opacity: 0; }
  .fade-2 { animation: fadeUp .6s ease .15s forwards; opacity: 0; }
  .fade-3 { animation: fadeUp .6s ease .25s forwards; opacity: 0; }
  .fade-4 { animation: fadeUp .6s ease .35s forwards; opacity: 0; }
  .fade-5 { animation: fadeUp .6s ease .45s forwards; opacity: 0; }
  @keyframes fadeUp { to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(14px); } }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media(max-width:700px) {
    .why-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.75rem; }
    .deliverable-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  @media(max-width:500px) {
    h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="https://expatbuildr.com" class="nav-logo">
      <div class="logo-mark"><img src="/logo.jpg" alt="ExpatBuildr" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;" /></div>
      <div class="logo-text">Expat<span>Buildr</span></div>
    </a>
    <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap: 1rem;">
      <div class="nav-badge">FREE RESOURCE</div>
      <button id="themeToggleBtn" aria-label="Toggle Theme" style="background:none;border:none;color:var(--text);cursor:pointer;font-size:1.1rem;display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0;outline:none;">
        <span class="sun-icon">☀</span>
        <span class="moon-icon">☾</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="free-tag fade-1">100% Free · No Credit Card · Instant Access</div>

    <h1 class="fade-2">
      The prompt that builds your<br />
      <em>entire content strategy</em><br />
      in 60 seconds.
    </h1>

    <p class="hero-sub fade-3">
      Copy one prompt. Paste it into any AI. Get a full lead generation post strategy for <strong style="color:var(--text)">X, LinkedIn, Reddit, TikTok, Instagram, and YouTube</strong> — tailored to your product, your audience, and your goal.
    </p>

    <div class="what-you-get fade-3">
      <div class="what-item">The Cold Traffic Prompt (copy-paste ready)</div>
      <div class="what-item">6-platform post strategy</div>
      <div class="what-item">Strategy dashboard access</div>
      <div class="what-item">Weekly founder briefings</div>
    </div>

    <!-- CAPTURE BOX -->
    <div class="capture-box fade-4">
      <div class="capture-label">// Get Instant Access</div>
      <div class="capture-headline">Drop your email.<br />Get the prompt immediately.</div>
      <div class="capture-sub">You'll get the prompt + dashboard access right away. Then weekly notes on building funnels that convert cold traffic without wasting ad spend.</div>

      <div class="field-wrap">
        <input class="email-input" type="email" id="hero-email" placeholder="your@email.com" autocomplete="email" />
        <button class="submit-btn" id="hero-btn">
          <span id="hero-btn-text">Send Me the Free Prompt →</span>
        </button>
        <div class="msg error" id="hero-error">Please enter a valid email address.</div>
        <div class="msg success" id="hero-success">✓ You're in! Opening your dashboard...</div>
      </div>
      <div class="capture-privacy">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime. Your email stays yours.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT YOU GET -->
<section id="what">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-tag">What's Inside</div>
    <h2>One prompt.<br /><em>Six platforms.</em><br />Zero guesswork.</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:.92rem;max-width:52ch;margin-top:.5rem">The prompt generates a full strategy for each platform — post angles, hooks, formats, and a posting cadence based on your niche.</p>

    <div class="deliverable-grid">
      <div class="deliv-item fade-up">
        <span class="deliv-icon">𝕏</span>
        <div class="deliv-platform">Twitter / X</div>
        <h3>Thread Hooks + Angles</h3>
        <p>Viral thread structures, reply strategies, and positioned posts that pull cold followers into your funnel.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="deliv-item fade-up">
        <span class="deliv-icon">in</span>
        <div class="deliv-platform">LinkedIn</div>
        <h3>Authority Posts + CTAs</h3>
        <p>Founder-voice posts that build credibility, drive profile visits, and convert connections to buyers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="deliv-item fade-up">
        <span class="deliv-icon">⬛</span>
        <div class="deliv-platform">Reddit</div>
        <h3>Community-Native Strategy</h3>
        <p>How to post in subreddits without getting banned — and funnel readers to your offer without being salesy.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="deliv-item fade-up">
        <span class="deliv-icon">♪</span>
        <div class="deliv-platform">TikTok</div>
        <h3>Short-Form Hook Scripts</h3>
        <p>Low-CPM acquisition scripts designed for Tier-2/3 geo-arbitrage. Cheap traffic, high-intent leads.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="deliv-item fade-up">
        <span class="deliv-icon">◻</span>
        <div class="deliv-platform">Instagram</div>
